Grinch = someone's who spoils their enjoyment or fun
Debunk = Something that is less important  or false or hallow
Vivify = To make something lively and interesting
silver tongue = someone who is elaquent or convincing in speaking 
ex: my father is "Silver tongue" person that he can convince my mother to do or to buy anything he wants.
Jannack = someone who is straight  forward and fair.
whimsy = something that is intended to be funny and stranger
Joyance = a feelinig of joy, glandene gladness or festivity
Turtle dove = A gentle and loving person
 

